<plot>His family, his wife Florence (Florence Lake), his mother-in-law (Dot Farley) and his know-it-all brother-in-law (Jack Rice), already disgusted that Edgar has bought a trailer to go on vacation, do nothing to bring any always-missing harmony into Edgar's life. Once on the road, turmoil and disaster follow, beginning with the simple act of opening the folding chairs.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?232905</url></doc>
